Length:
    0 characters. [single]
    1-9 characters. [property InvalidLength]
    10+ characters. [property ValidLength]

UppercaseContent:
    Less than two uppercase. [if ValidLength] [property MissingUppercase]
    2 or more uppercase. [property UppercasePassed]

SpecialContent:
    No special. [if ValidLength && UppercasePassed && !InvalidLength]
    At least one special. [property SpecialPassed]

NumericContent:
    No numbers. [if ValidLength && UppercasePassed && SpecialPassed && !InvalidLength]
    At least one number. [if !MissingUppercase] [else] [if UppercasePassed && SpecialPassed && !InvalidLength]